-No, no, I agree about that.

512
01:25:38.717 --> 01:25:39.884
Let's get on with it.

513
01:25:40.135 --> 01:25:42.804
Okay. But, look, Dave.

514
01:25:43.638 --> 01:25:46.266
Say we put the unit back
and it doesn't fail?

515
01:25:46.474 --> 01:25:49.686
That would pretty well wrap it up
as far as Hal is concerned.

516
01:25:51.396 --> 01:25:54.899
-We'd be in very serious trouble.
-We would, wouldn't we?

517
01:25:55.150 --> 01:25:56.776
What the hell can we do?

518
01:25:59.779 --> 01:26:03.867
-We wouldn't have too many alternatives.
-We wouldn't have any alternatives.

519
01:26:04.659 --> 01:26:08.663
