556
01:41:38.926 --> 01:41:40.719
What's the problem?

557
01:41:41.136 --> 01:41:44.348
<i>I think you know what the problem is
just as well as I do.</i>

558
01:41:44.556 --> 01:41:46.433
What are you talking about, Hal?

559
01:41:47.434 --> 01:41:51.522
<i>This mission is too important for me
to allow you to jeopardise it.</i>

560
01:41:52.606 --> 01:41:54.984
I don't know
what you're talking about, Hal.

561
01:41:56.986 --> 01:42:00.948
<i>I know that you and Frank
were planning to disconnect me...</i>

562
01:42:01.156 --> 01:42:03.951
<i>...and that's something
I cannot allow to happen.</i>

563
01:42:09.248 --> 01:42:11.125
Where did you get that idea, Hal?

564
01:42:11.667 --> 01:42:15.796
<i>Although you took very thorough
precautions in the pod...</i>

565
01:42:16.046 --> 01:42:18.257
<i>...against my hearing you...</i>

566
01:42:18.674 --> 01:42:20.968
<i>...I could see your lips move.</i>

567
01:42:33.022 --> 01:42:34.523
All right, Hal.

568
01:42:37.735 --> 01:42:40.571
I'll go in through
the emergency air lock.

569
01:42:42.114 --> 01:42:44.742
<i>Without your space helmet, Dave...</i>

570
01:42:45.242 --> 01:42:47.703
<i>...you're going to find that
rather difficult.</i>

571
01:42:48.871 --> 01:42:50.998
Hal, I won't argue with you anymore.

572
01:42:51.248 --> 01:42:52.333
Open the doors.

573
01:42:53.083 --> 01:42:54.335
<i>Dave...</i>

574
01:42:54.793 --> 01:42:59.256
<i>...this conversation can serve
no purpose anymore. Goodbye.</i>

575
