HAL: <i>Just what do you think
you're doing, Dave?</i>

585
01:50:00.927 --> 01:50:02.179
<i>Dave...</i>

586
01:50:03.388 --> 01:50:07.809
<i>...I really think I'm entitled
to an answer to that question.</i>

587
01:50:24.701 --> 01:50:28.246
<i>I know everything hasn't been
quite right with me...</i>

588
01:50:30.207 --> 01:50:32.626
<i>...but I can assure you now...</i>

589
01:50:33.710 --> 01:50:35.754
<i>...very confidently...</i>

590
01:50:37.506 --> 01:50:40.550
<i>...that it's going to be
all right again.</i>

591
01:50:44.054 --> 01:50:46.139
<i>I feel much better now.</i>

592
01:50:48.475 --> 01:50:50.519
<i>I really do.</i>

593
01:50:54.272 --> 01:50:55.982
<i>Look, Dave...</i>

594
01:50:57.943 --> 01:51:01.196
<i>...I can see you're
really upset about this.</i>

595
01:51:05.826 --> 01:51:09.538
<i>I honestly think you
ought to sit down calmly...</i>

596
01:51:10.163 --> 01:51:13.500
<i>...take a stress pill
and think things over.</i>

597
01:51:18.922 --> 01:51:23.301
<i>I know I've made some
very poor decisions recently...</i>

598
01:51:26.054 --> 01:51:29.391
<i>...but I can give you
my complete assurance...</i>

599
01:51:29.641 --> 01:51:32.686
<i>...that my work will be back to normal.</i>

600
01:51:36.648 --> 01:51:41.778
<i>I've still got the greatest enthusiasm
and confidence in the mission...</i>

601
01:51:43.321 --> 01:51:45.615
<i>...and I want to help you.</i>

602
01:51:50.078 --> 01:51:51.454
<i>Dave...</i>

603
01:51:52.581 --> 01:51:53.957
<i>...stop.</i>

604
01:51:58.211 --> 01:52:00.839
