619
01:53:45.276 --> 01:53:46.569
<i>I'm...</i>

620
01:53:47.487 --> 01:53:48.863
<i>...afraid.</i>

621
01:53:55.370 --> 01:53:57.414
<i>Good afternoon...</i>

622
01:53:58.415 --> 01:54:00.125
<i>...gentlemen.</i>

623
01:54:02.002 --> 01:54:07.132
<i>I am a HAL 9000 computer.</i>

624
01:54:09.300 --> 01:54:12.429
<i>I became operational...</i>

625
01:54:12.804 --> 01:54:16.641
<i>...at the HAL plant...</i>

626
01:54:16.850 --> 01:54:19.102
<i>...in Urbana, Illinois...</i>

627
01:54:19.602 --> 01:54:24.524
<i>...on the 12th of January, 1992.</i>

628
01:54:26.067 --> 01:54:29.738
<i>My instructor was Mr. Langley...</i>

629
01:54:30.363 --> 01:54:33.283
<i>...and he taught me to sing a song.</i>

630
01:54:34.993 --> 01:54:37.454
<i>If you'd like to hear it...</i>

631
01:54:37.912 --> 01:54:39.581
<i>...I can sing it for you.</i>

632
01:54:41.082 --> 01:54:43.918
Yes, I'd like to hear it, Hal.

633
01:54:44.586 --> 01:54:46.004
